uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.motor.match

Class DMatcherCustomiser<M extends DObject,Q extends M>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.motor.match.DMatcherCustomiser<M,Q>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DMatchAggregator, DMatchRangeOverlapper, DMatchSectionInverter

    public abstract class DMatcherCustomiser<M extends DObject,Q extends M>
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract base-class whose extensions provided specific customisations of the matching process, based on a particular domain-specific Object Model (OM).
